name: Space Labyrinth (IgorTheGameDeveloper)
description: Space Labyrinth is a single level game, made for Interstellar Game Jam 4. You play as Smileyball, a blue round alien who was mistakenly transported to a space labyrinth for prisoners in another dimension shortly before his wedding. Your goal is to help Smileyball escape the labyrinth and return to his home planet to his beloved girlfriend.
